; Regression test for issue #838: account directive not giving warning with --strict (BZ#838)
; https://github.com/ledger/ledger/issues/838
account Assets:Cash
account Expenses:Food
commodity $

2024/01/01 Test
    Expenses:Unknown    $5.00
    Assets:Cash

test bal --strict
              $-5.00  Assets:Cash
               $5.00  Expenses:Unknown
--------------------
                   0
__ERROR__
Warning: "$FILE", line 8: Unknown account 'Expenses:Unknown'
end test
